</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1">81583</post-id></item><item><title>GitHub Skyline CLI 拡張機能が利用可能になりました</title><link>https://github.blog/changelog/2024-12-09-github-skyline-cli-extension</link><dc:creator>Lee Reilly</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.blog/changelog/2024-12-02-auto-draft</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Bring your GitHub contributions to life with the new GitHub Skyline CLI extension – visualize, customize, and 3D print your journey in open source, all from the command line! 🛠️&amp;#8230;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.blog/changelog/2024-12-09-github-skyline-cli-extension&quot;&gt;GitHub Skyline CLI extension now available&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.blog&quot;&gt;The GitHub Blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
